        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Classroom Readiness Tax Relief Act of 2007 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to make permanent the tax deductions for: (1) certain expenses of elementary and secondary school teachers; and (2) corporate contributions of computer technology and equipment for educational purposes.</p>]]></text>
